# Auto-run after editing

After modifying any Python source file in `rk_flash_tool/`, automatically run the application:

```bash
cd /Users/kevin.zhuang/rk-flash-tool && source .venv/bin/activate && python -m rk_flash_tool
```

- Run in background (`block_until_ms: 0`) since it's a GUI app
- Check startup output after ~3 seconds to confirm no errors
- If there are import errors or crashes, fix them before reporting
